common.runtime.environment

Class ArgString

  • java.lang.Object
    • common.runtime.environment.ArgString
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    ApplicationArgString, StageArgString

    public class ArgString
extends java.lang.Object
    The ArgString class is class containing the string referencing the common command line argument(s) for a stage and an application.

    Vincent Mirian
    Date:
